    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/5d98b72b705e223916c39cdf32ce1bd6.poster.avif?t=1745736047\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/5d98b72b705e223916c39cdf32ce1bd6.webm?t=1745736047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/5d98b72b705e223916c39cdf32ce1bd6.mp4?t=1745736047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >四个角色和各种敌人</h2>与律、米拉和他们的盟友一起，与控制了新封建时代日本最强大忍者家族的邪恶教派展开激烈战斗。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/a172e61737eb6306c3ccf457edbaa7c3.poster.avif?t=1745736047\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/a172e61737eb6306c3ccf457edbaa7c3.webm?t=1745736047\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015720/extras/a172e61737eb6306c3ccf457edbaa7c3.mp4?t=1745736047\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人或本地合作模式</h2>在街机的本地合作模式中，您可以独自接受挑战，也可以叫上朋友一起玩。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握角色能力</h2>游戏中的可控角色有各种招式，从防御、闪避到攻击，都需要掌握，这样才能在与 Shobatsu 的强大敌人作战时取得优势。尤其是攻击招式，如果使用得当，可以打出既有冲击力又有趣的连击。不过，即使您已经成为战斗能手，在与 Shobatsu 的无情 Boss 搏斗时，也要做好接受严峻考验的准备。",
